latestPosts.caption:
When life was falling apart, love found a way. Manish and Nitesh met at a time when both were seeking comfort, companionship, and clarity — and what began as an unexpected connection quickly turned into the promise of a lifetime. From a sweet text proposal to a pastel-hued wedding on a serene farm, their journey was filled with warmth, honesty, and unwavering support. A celebration not just of love, but of courage, acceptance, and new beginnings.
